  %div.content
    %h2 Already know JS?
    %p
      We'd love to have people around to answer questions! We're looking for anyone who likes tutoring, knows JS, and would be willing to hang out with us some week(s) for our study group. There's no ongoing commitment, you're welcome to come once or many times. However, I don't want to waste your time by having a bunch of tutors waiting around for questions. So if there's enough interest, I'll add a cap of 2 tutors per week, and spread out the work.


